To run simply use node ./src/index.js in the terminal

Make sure to create an .env file with your
Discord token - DISCORD_TOKEN
OpenAi token - OPENAI_TOKEN
How you want chatgpt to act - CHARACTER
and the prefix to talk to the bot - PREFIX

Make sure to change the gpt version to the one you want. GPT-3.5-turbo is recommended as its cheap, but for some projects you'll ned GPT-4 for its more up to date information. 

Also make sure you have node.js installed otherwise it wont work
